          {
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 2 of SLEEP: A 30-Day Tapping Intensive. The script targets the body that holds on even after the mind has quietened, the muscles that grip through the night, the back that won't release into the mattress, the legs that stay tight. Use it lying down, at bedtime, when the physical holding is what's standing between you and sleep.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
